description = "A pair of night vision goggles. They are waterproof obviously. Theres a empty slot in it. Can be equipped."
shopDescription = "You look like you could use some night vision goggles. These babies will help you see in the dark. There's even a mode for color! or there would be if they weren't broken. But hey, I'll give you a good price on them anyways. Considering you don't have a submarine with giant headlights I think you'll need them.";